# Interview Quick Notes

### Flexbox vs Grid

| Flexbox       | Grid             |
| ------------- | ---------------- |
| 1D Layout     | 2D Layout        |
| Row OR Column | Rows AND Columns |
| Navbar        | Dashboard        |
| Buttons       | Gallery          |

